          <br> username: guest | password: guest</p>
        <p class="detail-text">
          The email campaign is designed to drive team members to the site where they can access articles, project updates, interviews of other team members and internal culture articles. I used data from our Mailchimp campaign to inform the design between issues, resulting in a design that focused on clear calls to action and brevity. In our last campaign, we doubled our opens and got the vast majority of recipients to click through to the main site.  
